Get-NetIPAddress
    - Displays all IP addresses assigned to network adapters.

Get-DnsClientServerAddress
    - Shows configured DNS servers for every adapter.

Get-NetRoute
    - Displays the Windows routing table.

Get-NetAdapter
    - Lists all network adapters and their status.

Restart-NetAdapter -Name Ethernet
    - Disables and re-enables a network adapter.

Test-Connection google.com
    - Performs a PowerShell ping test.

Test-NetConnection google.com -Port 443
    - Tests network connectivity to a specific TCP port. Excellent for troubleshooting firewalls.
